{
  "version": "0.4",
  "title": "XCP Thank You / Confirmation Page",
  "type": "page",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "thankyou_hero",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Thank You Hero",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "content_position": "middle"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "thankyou_hero_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_eyebrow",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Enquiry Received</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Thank You — I'll Be in Touch Shortly",
                "header_size": "h1",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_intro",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Your enquiry has been received. I personally read every message and typically respond within 24 hours, Monday to Friday. Look out for a reply from info@xcphotography.co.uk — check your junk folder just in case.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "thankyou_next_steps",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "What Happens Next",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "structure": "30"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "thankyou_step1_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 33
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_step1_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "1. I Read Your Enquiry",
                "header_size": "h3",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_step1_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Every enquiry is read personally. I will review your project brief and consider how I can best serve your goals.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "thankyou_step2_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 33
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_step2_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "2. Discovery Call",
                "header_size": "h3",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_step2_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Within 24 hours I will reply to propose a short discovery call — no obligation, no sales pitch. Just an honest conversation about your vision and how photography can serve it.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "thankyou_step3_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 33
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_step3_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "3. Your Proposal",
                "header_size": "h3",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_step3_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>After our call, I will send a personalised proposal covering the shoot concept, deliverables, timeline, and investment. You choose whether to proceed — on your terms, in your own time.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "thankyou_explore",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "While You Wait — Explore",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "structure": "30"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "thankyou_explore_col1",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 33,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_portfolio_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Browse the Portfolio",
                "header_size": "h4",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_portfolio_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "View Portfolio",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/portfolio",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "thankyou_explore_col2",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 33,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_services_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Explore Services",
                "header_size": "h4",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_services_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "View Services",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/services",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "thankyou_explore_col3",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 33,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "thankyou_about_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Read My Story",
                "header_size": "h4",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "thankyou_about_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "About Xavier",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/about",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
